578  kmer = 0;
579  for(cns->qtop=0;cns->qtop<cns->g->ksize;cns->qtop++){
580  kmer = (kmer << 2) | qry[cns->qtop];
581  }
582  cns->g->kmers->buffer[0].mer = kmer;
583  u = get_dbgcnskmerhash(cns->g->khash, 0);
584  if(u == NULL) return 0;
585  kidx = *u;
586  dp = next_ref_dbgcnsdpv(cns->dps);
587  dp->kidx = kidx;
588  dp->path = DBGCNS_PATH_M;
589  dp->qpos = cns->qtop;
590  dp->score = 0;
591  dp->bt_idx = 0;
592  array_heap_push(cns->heap->buffer, cns->heap->size, cns->heap->cap, uint32_t, cns->dps->size - 1, num_cmp(cns->dps->buffer[b].score, cns->dps->buffer[a].score));
593  // dbg traversing
594  while(cns->heap->size){
595  status = dbg_cns_core(cns);
596  if(status == DBGCNS_CNS_HIT){
597  dp_idx = cns->heap->buffer[0];
598  array_heap_remove(cns->heap->buffer, cns->heap->size, cns->heap->cap, uint32_t, 0, num_cmp(cns->dps->buffer[b].score, cns->dps->buffer[a].score));
599  dp = ref_dbgcnsdpv(cns->dps, dp_idx);
600  if(dp->score > cns->max_score){
601  cns->max_score = dp->score;
602  cns->best_idx = dp_idx;
603  }
604  }
605  }
606  if(cns->best_idx == 0) return 0;
607  // traceback to get cns seq
608  dp_idx = cns->best_idx;
609  while(dp_idx){
610  dp = ref_dbgcnsdpv(cns->dps, dp_idx);
611  push_u1v(cns->cigars, dp->path);
612  cns->alns[dp->path] ++;
613  if(dp->path != DBGCNS_PATH_I){
614  k = ref_dbgcnskmerv(cns->g->kmers, dp->kidx);
615  push_u1v(cns->cns, k->mer & 0x03);
616  if(k->cov == 1){
617  add_char_string(cns->seq, "acgt"[k->mer & 0x03]);
618  } else {
619  add_char_string(cns->seq, "ACGT"[k->mer & 0x03]);
620  }
621  }
622  dp_idx = dp->bt_idx;
623  }
624  // first ksize - 1 bases may be not corrected, truncated
625  reverse_string(cns->seq);
626  reverse_u1v(cns->cns);
627  reverse_u1v(cns->cigars);
628  return cns->seq->size;
629 }
